{"tid":53860,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"人越大好似越少朋友","createTime":"2016-12-25T05:02:18.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-25T08:01:46.000Z","uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4ff41b9494daad808f99de0122758f8d0bd7d922","tid":53860,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T05:02:18.000Z","msg":"手機有一半或以上既聯絡人根本上唔會聯絡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  再fd底既朋友都各有各忙 返學既返學 返工既返工 有時一個月聚到兩三次已經好好 有冇有同感既巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0de3be341c2b77b10bf4d94b841e07906c7141fb","tid":53860,"uid":13013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T05:03:45.000Z","msg":"認同 但自己主動都好緊要"},{"pid":"f227df5c640bd573e6736712e03c660fc4b1ed14","tid":53860,"uid":25945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T05:05:41.000Z","msg":"人愈大愈少朋友，不是你人際關係變差，而是你懂得選擇誰能做你的真正朋友。"},{"pid":"5660091fdab84384a2e757d6a2f2c84a56cb4eba","tid":53860,"uid":40308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T05:08:13.000Z","msg":"朋友多少真係好睇你自己性格"},{"pid":"123f3da8939a7b50d87b7caf28099014d3f00aa9","tid":53860,"uid":30552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T07:44:25.000Z","msg":"本身都唔怕孤獨，可以自己行街自己食飯。當然會有想見朋友嘅時候，但我都好需要有自己時間。要我每個星期六日都見朋友嘅話我會好攰。而友情係需要維持，所以朋友真係貴精不貴多。"},{"pid":"5c8d1bef262868eadf775eef00b366ce75e368be","tid":53860,"uid":28960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T07:51:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8564c0ed62fd97416440d8d9ea6c4e3cb119c701","tid":53860,"uid":68255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T07:56:52.000Z","msg":"越向著青春走遠 越容易孤單 你可有發現 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de19510d8a113aaa6d0d1534edf6d9cc16ea4db4","tid":53860,"uid":24335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T08:01:46.000Z","msg":"位置變了, 各有隊友<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家連想搵d 舊同學舊朋友都驚自己阻到佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}